1. *Onako* je rekao da će biti tu. (He said he will be there like that.)
2. Njegov govor je bio *onako* vatren. (His speech was so fiery.)
3. Ne znam *onako* kako da se postavim. (I don't know how to position myself like that.)
4. Podelili smo se *onako* kako smo dogovorili. (We parted in a way we had agreed on.)
5. *Onako*, kako smo se zapoznali. (Like that, how we got acquainted.)
6. Njegov glas je zvučao *onako*. (His voice sounded like that.)